{"tid":365871,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"【Orage台】你估我真係知自己做緊咩?  Day92 19/8","createTime":"2017-08-19T14:47:09.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-19T17:45:47.000Z","uid":122942,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"317d57372a0f4b05e5dae81d06516d8304ca546b","tid":365871,"uid":122942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T14:47:09.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/5ADqP2.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2F5ADqP2.gif&h=8c5a58f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大家好，我係Orage。 我會於每晚11點至2點開台玩遊戲同與觀眾聊天。<br />\n因為我極度3分鐘熱度，所以好少會一直玩同一隻Game。<br />\n有興趣嘅巴打入黎捧下場，一齊傾下計啦  <br />\n<br />\n今晚11點左右見 <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.twitch.tv/oragejan \" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.twitch.tv%2Foragejan%20&d=VoAUQLZYd%2Fi1HvvGMv7jAHIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=0111c4b7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.twitch.tv/oragejan </a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/W4CK8P.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2FW4CK8P.png&h=69cccb5f&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n另外我開左個FB專頁，開台前或者有任何突發事唔開都會Po上FB。<br />\n有時會PO日常野同覺得有趣嘅事，希望巴打們可以入黎比個讚。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/oragejan\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Foragejan&d=VoAUQLZYd%2Fi1HvvGMv7jAHIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=ba8aae40\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/oragejan</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/NRSeWz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2FNRSeWz.jpg&h=f4a261d8&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n另外我亦開左個Youtuber Page放開台嘅Backup<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCa49ivSXtdCYwObEq9pRLSg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fchannel%2FUCa49ivSXtdCYwObEq9pRLSg&d=VoAUQLZYd%2Fi1HvvGMv7jAHIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=070d0b0c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCa49ivSXtdCYwObEq9pRLSg</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">請各位多多支持，比D錢黎洗下</span></span></div>"},{"pid":"f3a97224b62f70e9ae92c44c2ab80ea8647a9129","tid":365871,"uid":122942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T15:07:44.000Z","msg":"已開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6fc552dee7c7d602cfb4088b3624b9a5c227045","tid":365871,"uid":122942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T15:13:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19956f3d27f8fc190c66d67d697f0eb29e7a6d5e","tid":365871,"uid":122942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T15:18:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db4016cc76ce00c514e05ae84e27c4d09b7624e3","tid":365871,"uid":122942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T15:20:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75de97eab565695016e0990963a58e0aa06f5734","tid":365871,"uid":122942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T15:23:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7293e6b9eab2d11c5d6cea25409478eb4a77db06","tid":365871,"uid":122942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T15:27:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6cba28101c2861707a1d0c0e677eef2f92feed35","tid":365871,"uid":122942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T15:28:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2bcf3f2f7380648058310c652447f965b829919","tid":365871,"uid":122942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T15:33:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\